                    },
                    "body": "Hi Anthony,\r\nyou're right, but HTML5 brings some changes: [http:\/\/www.whatwg.org\/specs\/web-apps\/current-work\/multipage\/number-state.html#reset-button-state]\r\n\r\nCan you add a patch for the current version 1.11?\r\nLater, for version 2, we must consider HTML5.\r\n\r\nThanks and greetings\r\nKaiuwe",
